-- Mineworker Killed in a Blast at South Africa's Tau Lekoa, Labor Union Says
-- Alastair Reed
-- 2010-07-08T07:34:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/mineworker-killed-in-a-blast-at-south-africa-s-tau-lekoa-labor-union-says.html

          
          
             A mineworker was killed in an
explosion at the Tau Lekoa mine in South Africa, the National
Union of Mineworkers said in an e-mailed statement today.  
          
          


  


        